snippet.title: Trivia Beta Party | V5 Release Trailer + Download
snippet.description:
The mod released on July 27th, 2023 and is being uploaded to celebrate the 2 year anniversary of the mod's original version on November 17th, 2021. V5 was the final version planned and will not be getting any more updates. 
---
"Welcome To Trivia Beta Party!" Partake in a modded take of Jackbox Games' Trivia Murder Party 2 based around @Beta64 's community. Featuring the voice talents of @Cashspoon and other key community members (@Dizmond ,@hexenhell , @jjdb211_bad , Chips McGee, SuperMarioBrosFan116, ScottNoLastName, and @RainbowKappa ) , You'll try not to die in new , yet questionable ways as you answer community-centric trivia in hopes you won't die at this totally real BetaCon Convention! 

---
Watch @Beta64 's Live Playthrough : 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=av9JxhlmNaE&pp=ygUQamFja2JveCBiZXRhIG1vZA%3D%3D

Download Trivia Beta64 Party V5 :
https://github.com/rainbowkappamc/jackboxbeta64

https://play.kappabox.live/
---
Why is this being uploaded this late after being released? :
I never did post this to inform the non-Beta64 audience that this mod was released so I wanted to do this eventually. This was the final trailer as a way to celebrate the mod's release and was shown on Beta64's stream the night before he streamed it and for us to release it officially.
